≠…–Z<?php exit; ?>a:1:{s:7:"content";O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:4:"1512";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2018-03-02 21:01:16";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2018-03-02 15:16:16";s:12:"post_content";s:9358:"<p style="text-align: justify;">She is not only an incredibly fabulous actress but also she is a fierce military recruit which makes this gorgeous badass actress totally different from everyone present in the entertainment world. we are here talking about the one and only¬†<strong><em>Gal Gadot</em></strong>.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><em>Gal Gadot-Varsano</em></strong> was born on 30 April 1985 in a city of Israel, Petah Tikva as a first child to mother Irit who is a teacher and an engineer father Micheal Gadot. She also has a younger sister named Dana Gadot. In high school, Biology was her major subject and began studying at IDC Herzliya College before pursuing her passion for modeling and acting.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Career</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>As a model</strong></p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1514" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/4506-300x194.jpg" alt="" width="546" height="353" />
<p style="text-align: justify;">Gadot won the 2004 <strong><em>Miss Israel beauty pageant</em></strong> and then competed in <strong><em>Miss Universe 2004</em></strong> held in Ecuador which marked the beginning of her modeling career. In 2007, she was in Maxim Photo Shoot, <strong><em>‚ÄúWomen of the IDF‚Äù</em></strong> and was featured on the cover of <strong><em>The New York Post</em></strong>.¬† She also has been associated in many Israeli and American campaigns as a model for <strong><em>Miss Sixty</em></strong>, <strong><em>Huawei Smartphones</em></strong>, <strong><em>Gucci fragrances</em></strong>, <strong><em>Vine Vera Skincare ranges</em></strong>, <strong><em>Captain Morgan rum</em></strong> and <strong><em>Jaguar Cars</em></strong>. Then, she was featured as a cover girl in many renowned magazines such as <strong><em>Cosmopolitan</em></strong>, <strong><em>Glamour</em></strong>, <strong><em>Bride Magazine</em></strong>, <strong><em>UMM,</em></strong> <strong><em>Cleo</em></strong>, <strong><em>Entertainment Weekly</em></strong>, <strong><em>Fashion</em></strong>, <strong><em>Lucire </em></strong>and many more. Eventually, from 2008 to 2016 she was the face for fashion brand <strong><em>Castro</em></strong>.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>As an actor</strong></p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1515" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wonder_woman_gal_gadot-2048x1536-300x194.jpg" alt="" width="545" height="353" />
<p style="text-align: justify;">Gal Gadot is associated in Television as well. She has acted in some few episodes of television series like <strong><em>Entourage</em></strong> (2009), <strong><em>The Beautiful Life</em></strong> (2009), <strong><em>Asfur</em></strong> (2011), <strong><em>Kathmandu</em></strong> (2012) and <strong><em>Eretz Nehederet </em></strong>(2012).</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">The Israeli actress got her first audition call from a cast director for the movie Quantum of Solace but sadly she didn‚Äôt get the role. She then acted in an Israeli film <strong><em>Bubot</em></strong> in 2008. Later, after a few months, she was casted by the same cast director of Quantum of Solace and thus, debuted in Hollywood as Gisele Yashar in the movie <strong><em>Fast and Furious</em></strong> which was the fourth movie in <strong><em>The Fast and Furious Franchise</em></strong> where she splendidly performed all her stunts. She reprised her role in <strong><em>Fast Five</em></strong> as well as <strong><em>Fast and Furious 6</em></strong> in the year 2011 and 2013 respectively.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Gal then was seen in many movies such as an American comedy movie <strong><em>Date Night</em></strong> (2010), an American action comedy <strong><em>Knight and Day</em></strong> (2010), an Israeli comedy sports film <strong><em>Kicking Out Shoshana </em></strong>(2014), an American crime thriller <strong><em>Triple 9</em></strong> (2016), an American- British action crime thriller <strong><em>Criminal</em></strong> (2016) along with an American action comedy film <strong><em>Keeping Up with the Joneses </em></strong>(2016).</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1517" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/keeping-up-with-the-joneses-2880x1800-jon-hamm-gal-gadot-6205-e1520003345155-300x190.jpg" alt="" width="541" height="342" />
<p style="text-align: justify;">Though she had huge potential, she was not able to get roles that would best depict her talent. Later in 2016 she landed the role of Diana Prince/ Wonder Women which proved to be her breakthrough role in the movie <strong><em>Batman vs Superman: Dawn of Justice</em></strong> under <strong><em>DC Extended Universe</em></strong> which was one of the highest grossing movies of the year. Subsequently, in the following year, she reprised the role in a solo movie <strong><em>Wonder Women</em></strong> and <strong><em>Justice League</em></strong>. Recently, in an interview in <em><strong>Jimmy Kimmel</strong></em> Live she told that she almost didn‚Äôt get her dream role due to her small breasts ergo, Gal had done a lot of physical training to do justice to her superhero role in the movies and consequently the movies were a huge success and her acting and stunt skills were widely acclaimed.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Upcoming Projects</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Gadot astonishing performance as Wonder Women opened many doors of opportunities in this industry.¬† She is set to reprise her role of Wonder Women in big budget movies <strong><em>Justice League Part 2</em></strong> and <strong><em>Wonder Women Part 2</em></strong> which will be released in 2019. Other than this, she will also be a part of thriller war movie <strong><em>Ruin</em></strong> in 2018. Gal will also be seen in a thriller drama movie <strong><em>Deeper</em></strong> alongside Bradley Cooper and an action adventure fantasy movie <strong><em>Flashpoint,</em></strong> both of which will be released in 2020.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1518" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/landscape-1495182499-gal-gadot-wonder-woman-300x140.jpg" alt="" width="544" height="254" />
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Personal Life</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Gal Gadot along with her husband <strong><em>Yaron Varsano</em></strong> whom she married in 2008 used to own a luxury hotel in Tel Aviv, Israel until 2015 and now they along with their two beautiful daughters live in Israel. The couple own property in Los Angeles as well.¬† She served for two years in Israel Defense force as a combat instructor. It is also reported that she was 5 months pregnant during reshoots for Wonder Women.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1519" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/5d1e321a64e08954643e15264820d224-300x187.jpg" alt="" width="537" height="335" />
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Achievements</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Gadot has been highly admired for her beauty as well as her acting skills time and again. In 2012 she was ranked on Number 5 on the list of <strong><em>50 most intelligent, funny and gorgeous Jewish Women in the World </em></strong>by Shalom Life. She was awarded <strong><em>Most Popular US Actress in China</em></strong> by <strong><em>Chinese American Film Festival</em></strong> for her role in <strong><em>Batman vs Superman: Dawn of Justice</em></strong> in 2016. Moreover, Gal‚Äôs role in Wonder Women made her to be honored with <strong><em>Choice Movie: Actress Awards</em></strong>, <strong><em>Spotlight Award</em></strong>, <strong><em>Rising Star Award-Actress</em></strong>, and <strong><em>Virtuosos Award</em></strong> from <strong><em>Teen Choice Awards</em></strong>, <strong><em>National Board of Review Awards</em></strong>, <strong><em>Palm Spring International Film Awards</em></strong> as well as <strong><em>Santa Barbara Film Festival</em></strong> respectively in 2018.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1520" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/653320_thump-300x179.jpg" alt="" width="536" height="320" />
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Net Worth</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Gal Gadot has been ranked in the third position in <strong><em>the highest grossing actor list </em></strong>by Forbes in 2017. She is just behind Vin Diesel and Dwayne Johnson with $1.4 billion in global ticket sales between Wonder Women and Justice League leaving behind her other female stars like <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/daisy-jazz-isobel-ridley-career-future-projects-personal-life-achievements-networth/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Daisy Ridley</a> and Emma Watson. The net worth of Gadot is reported to be $8 million.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Though Gadot had a bumpy journey at the beginning of her career, she is now rising so as to achieve her well-deserved position as one of the A-list actors in Hollywood. This stunning actress has a lot of great movies in her bag and we are pretty sure that this will help her reach spectacular heights in her career.</p>
